      ***X-Bones G66v2***
***Mission description***    Intercepted radio signals indicate scores of vicious pirates that are prolific throughout this system have turned mercenary & are now allied with the enemy. This dangerous union is seriously impeding our efforts to bring peace & stability to the system & its neighbors, in recent days attacks on our allies in this quadrant have doubled. We must gain control at all costs before this chaos spreads like a cancer across the galaxy.
***Mission objectives***    Seek & Destroy the enemys main base & all remote enemy installations. Seize the pirates hidden bunker & commandeer their custom vehicles & weapons. Stop them before they collect the bio-metal bounty for your squadrons heads.               *concept: SquareEyes*
